  m_text: "Highlights a \"suggested\" transform from hitting a Scene anchor, i.e.
    how best to \"place an app/widget\" on a surface. \n\nWhen hitting vertical surfaces;
    Y is world-up, Z is surface normal.\nWhen hitting horizontal surfaces; Y is world-up,
    Z is best-guess at player-facing."
